请伤一专人加以校对，不要错误。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"1237cace97"},{"id":"9534ed722d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"1237cace97"},{"id":"b9c211cd76","type":"paragraph","text":"二月六日下午十时","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"1237cace97"},{"id":"808f2b0162","type":"paragraph","text":"我所说的上级领导机关，是指党和政府的中央一级机关、大区一级机关、省（市）一级机关、专区一级机关和县级机关，这五级机关内都有不少的官主义，它们只注重布置工作，不注重检查工作。有些领导机关则有强追命令的作风，甚至包藏有违法乱纪分子。“","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"1237cace97"},{"id":"c33729ddb6","type":"subtitle","text":"三","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"1237cace97"},{"id":"0e6628c2a7","type":"paragraph","text":"李维汉、徐冰同志","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"1237cace97"},{"id":"768daba988","type":"paragraph","text":"今天下午三时有安子文批评管主义的报告，请通知中央一级（党政军及各民【主】党派人民团体）部长副部长等干部一律参加非病不许缺席。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"1237cace97"},{"id":"1bed4f829a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"1237cace97"},{"id":"c0d4b94e00","type":"paragraph","text":"二月七日上午九时","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"1237cace97"}],"page":{"id":"0af774e274","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"1237cace97","start":470,"end":471}}}},"__N_SSG":true}